'''MX Player'''是由印度公司MX Media & Entertainment（前身为J2 Interactive<ref>{{Cite news|date=2018-06-28|title=Times Internet buys MX Player for Rs 1,000 crore|work=The Economic Times|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/small-biz/startups/newsbuzz/times-internet-buys-mx-player-for-rs-1000-crore/articleshow/64773344.cms?from=mdr|access-date=2020-06-30|archive-date=2022-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123222012/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/small-biz/startups/newsbuzz/times-internet-buys-mx-player-for-rs-1000-crore/articleshow/64773344.cms?from=mdr}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Ramachandran|first=Naman|last2=Ramachandran|first2=Naman|date=2018-12-05|title=ATF: MX Player Reveals Ambitious Plans as India Streamer (EXCLUSIVE)|url=https://variety.com/2018/digital/asia/mx-player-india-streaming-platform-1203080697/|access-date=2020-06-30|website=Variety|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129210048/https://variety.com/2018/digital/asia/mx-player-india-streaming-platform-1203080697/|dead-url=no}}</ref>）开发的視頻播放軟件和[[OTT服务|OTT服务]]平台，它在全球拥有超过2.8亿用户<ref>{{Cite web|title=India’s MX Player expands to US, UK and other markets in international push|url=https://social.techcrunch.com/2020/03/26/indias-mx-player-expands-to-us-uk-and-other-markets-in-international-push/|access-date=2020-06-30|website=TechCrunch|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=MX Player top entertainment app in India in 2019|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/2020/mar/30/mx-player-top-entertainment-app-in-india-in-2019-2123519.html|access-date=2020-06-30|website=The New Indian Express|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018164043/https://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/2020/mar/30/mx-player-top-entertainment-app-in-india-in-2019-2123519.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，擁有超过15万小时的12种语言的流媒体库。该軟件目前以广告作為利潤來源，MX Player可以在iOS、Android和网頁上使用。

MX Player于2011年7月18日推出，當時它還只是一款视频播放軟件。它的特点是支持視頻字幕和可离线觀看视频。

2018年，{{link-en|Times Internet}}以1.4亿美元收购了MX Media & Entertainment的多数股权<ref>{{Cite web|title=India’s Times Internet buys popular video app MX Player for $140M to get into streaming|url=https://social.techcrunch.com/2018/06/27/times-internet-buys-mx-player-for-140m/|access-date=2020-06-27|website=TechCrunch|language=en-US}}</ref>。

2019年2月20日，MX Player推出了可收看原创节目的[[OTT服务|OTT服务]]平台。它拥有来自印度和国际多家电影公司的授权的視頻，包括{{link-en|FilmRise}}、{{link-en|Sonar Entertainment}}、{{link-en|Screen Media Films}}、Goldmine、{{link-en|Hungama Digital Media Entertainment}}, {{link-en|Shemaroo}}、[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]和[[索尼娱乐|索尼娱乐]].<ref>{{Cite web|last=Bureau|first=Our|title=MX Player inks content deal with Paramount Pictures and Sony Pictures Television India|url=https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/info-tech/mx-player-inks-content-deal-with-paramount-pictures-and-sony-pictures-television-india/article31268871.ece|access-date=2020-06-30|website=@businessline|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125053032/https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/info-tech/mx-player-inks-content-deal-with-paramount-pictures-and-sony-pictures-television-india/article31268871.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

2019年10月，MX Player在[[腾讯|腾讯]]领投的投资中筹集了1.108亿美元<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tencent leads $111M investment in India’s video streaming service MX Player|url=https://social.techcrunch.com/2019/10/29/tencent-times-internet-mx-player/|access-date=2020-06-30|website=TechCrunch|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Deal Street: Tencent Enters India’s Video Streaming Space With $110-Million Investment|url=https://www.bloombergquint.com/technology/startup-funding-news-mx-player-elasticrun-smartworks-fasal-fisdom|access-date=2020-06-30|website=BloombergQuint|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027044547/https://www.bloombergquint.com/technology/startup-funding-news-mx-player-elasticrun-smartworks-fasal-fisdom|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
